🌍 Global Water Consumption Dashboard – Power BI

This interactive dashboard presents a detailed analysis of global water consumption using data sourced from Kaggle. It visualizes how water is used across different countries and sectors, helping users identify patterns, inefficiencies, and sustainability concerns.

🔎 Dashboard Features:
Usage Breakdown by sector: Agriculture, Industry, Domestic

Top Water-Consuming Countries highlighted for comparison

Regional Filters for focused insights

Time Trends showing changes in consumption over the years

Clean, user-friendly layout with interactive visuals for exploration

🎯 Objective:
To raise awareness about water resource usage globally and support informed decision-making in sustainability and environmental planning.

🛠 Tools Used:
Power BI for data modeling, DAX, and visualizations

Excel for data cleaning

Kaggle as the data source

